creator: SHIMANO INC.
descriptionHtml:
Maximize Your Bike Performance.
With the smartphone app, you can easily update firmware and customize electric shifting in addition to the e-bike assist power program.

-Maximize the trail ride with customized settings in your own image.

-AUTOMATIC SHIFTING not requiring any gear shifting operation is comfortable. But to make the shift timing a bit quicker, change the timing to your preference with the app.
Ride comfortably even in a city with many traffic lights since it automatically switches to your favorite gear when stopping.
descriptionShort: Customize DI2 electric shifting in addition to the E-BIKE assist power program.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Adapted for EP8 Series (DU-EP800/SC-EM800/SW-EM800-L/EW-SW300)
-New simply user interface layout.(Current settings summary can be seen on the top page.)
-Update information is now displayed.(Firmware update information will pop-up when available.)
-Possible to connect with registered bicycle.( *All functions can be fully used by registering at SHIMANO ID)
